OL,5,G2300 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FA 41-year-old man is thrown 10
OL,7,     Ffeet in the air after a motorbike
OL,8,     Faccident, leaving him critically
OL,9,     Finjured. A five-year-old girl
OL,10,     Fsuffers a terrifying seizure,
OL,11,     Fpossibly caused by sepsis.
